data.description: Nestled in the coveted community of The Colony in Holbrook, this exquisite townhouse for sale is a haven of luxury and comfort. Boasting the highly sought-after Fairfield 4 model, this end unit residence offers a spacious layout with four bedrooms and two and a half baths, spanning over 2600 square feet. Upon entry, be greeted by a grand two-story foyer and living room adorned with a charming fireplace, perfect for cozy gatherings. The updated eat-in kitchen is a culinary dream, featuring granite countertops, top-of-the-line stainless steel appliances, and stylish ceramic tile floors and backsplash. Oversized primary bedroom with a large walk-in closet, en suite bath with Jacuzzi tub, and a sitting area that overlooks the yard. Convenience meets elegance with a first-floor laundry room, custom paint and moldings, luxury vinyl flooring, LED hi hats, built-in surround sound, Lutron switches, an Ecobee smart thermostat, and a high efficiency central air conditioning unit. With beautiful chandeliers and light fixtures adorning the space, along with ceiling fans and several fireplaces throughout, every corner exudes warmth and sophistication. Additionally, custom blinds and window treatments ensure privacy and style, while replacement windows offer efficiency and tranquility. A large beautiful stone patio and fenced yard overlooks the pond, giving you a beautiful and peaceful oasis. Don't miss the opportunity to call this remarkable property home.
